Package: libsecutils2
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Suggests: libuta
Description: OpenSSL enhancement wrapper library
 This provides utilities for
 credential loading and storage with optional integrity protection,
 certificate validation including status checks using CRLs and/or OCSP,
 TLS connection and configuration file handling helpers, and logging.
 This aims at simplifying use of commonly needed functionality.

Package: libsecutils-dev
Depends: libsecutils2 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}, libssl-dev
Suggests: libuta-dev
Section: devel
Architecture: any
Description: libsecutils C headers and documentation
 Development support for libsecutils

Package: libsecutils-bin
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Section: utils
